  • Method Details

    • onTrigger

      SongResult onTrigger(double mana, Profile profile)
      Called when the ability is triggered by a player ("Caster")
      Parameters:
      mana - The amount of mana that the caster has.
      profile - The profile of the caster.
      Returns:
      Returns a "SongResult." First two terms are this and profile, then the amount of mana the song requires, then whether the ability was successful. Or leave blank for success without taking mana.

    • triggerOnCooldown

      boolean triggerOnCooldown(Profile profile)
      This will be called when songs are triggered while on "cooldown"
      Returns:
      FALSE to send cooldown message, TRUE to avoid it.
